**1\. Features Overview**

**1a. Student Services Page / For Student’s Page**  
*For unsigned students/users of the application:*  
![][image1]![][image2]  
Resources for prospective students, parents, family, fans, alumni, and guests are readily available upon downloading the OSU app.

*For signed students of the application:*  
![][image3]![][image4]![][image5]  
Students are provided the listed services:

- Check their meal plan balance  
- View their recent campus transactions  
- Scan-in to the Colvin Recreation Center  
- Lock their lost/stolen student ID  
- Sign up for LASSO tutoring sessions  
- Change their O-Key account password

**1b. Academics Page**  
*For unsigned students/users of the application:*  
![][image6]![][image7]  
Students are prompted to connect to Canvas. Information regarding OSU academics is available to prospective students. The current semester’s academic calendar is available to the user, including redirections to the OSU site.

*For signed students of the application:*  
![][image8]![][image9]![][image10]![][image11]  
Students are provided a calendar in which they can add and remove tasks. Signed students are allowed to view their courses and various information regarding their courses. OSU academic calendar is still available for signed students.

**1c. Activity Feed Page**  
A fully functional activity feed page can be viewed by all users. Posting privileges are granted by the admin and intended for student organizations, OSU-related departments, OSU-affiliated teams, people of importance, etc. It is not intended for general student use. Users granted access to post can create personal profiles viewable by all users.

**1d. Campus Map Page**  
Features the web UI of the OSU campus map found online wrapped into the mobile application with embedded JS scripts.  
![][image15]

**1e. Resources Page**  
Includes groups of searchable OSU resources for student support, OSU safety, scholarships & grants, employment & work-study, research, and AI. Each resource directs users to the OSU website upon selection.
